data.description: Pre-Construction. To be built. Explore this beautiful Pearl home, ready for quick move-in. Structural features include a fourth bedroom and third bath in lieu of a study and powder room, an impressive kitchen with quartz countertops and a center island, a generous loft, a convenient laundry room with a sink, a lavish owner’s suite showcasing a private bath and oversized walk-in closet, a covered patio and a 3-car garage. This home also offers tile flooring on the main level, double sinks in both upstairs bathrooms and marble countertops in all three bathrooms. Tour today!    Features:    Cultured marble bathroom countertops  9' main-floor ceilings  10-year limited structural warranty  8' main-floor doors  Quartz kitchen countertops
